title: Leave a Legacy of Faith
itunes:title: Leave a Legacy of Faith
description:
Jesus won the victory. Now let’s take the power He has given us and not only win for ourselves but let’s help someone else to win. Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
